    "This finding showcases a similar behavior to our results.",
    "However, it should be noted that our system is operated at high packing fractions and is highly sensitive to the spatial configuration of the obstacles, not merely the lattice density.",
    "Therefore, a complete theoretical description of anomalous diffusions of CAPs remains an open question.",
    "In case (2), individual CAPs are subjected to a constant force field.",
    "When the reduced persistence length l p is small, CAPs and ABPs are similarly locked along the symmetry axes of the obstacle lattice."
